{"tid":1871040,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國際郵輪協會禁中港澳客登船","createTime":"2020-02-09T08:23:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T09:20:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c103f31571c4870593cfcff077a584605670cc6a","tid":1871040,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:23:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200209/E5HU4TSHTQM6MNEJMYEMLZG45E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200209%2FE5HU4TSHTQM6MNEJMYEMLZG45E%2F&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=173d14a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200209%2FE5HU4TSHTQM6MNEJMYEMLZG45E%2F&h=88f805b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200209/E5HU4TSHTQM6MNEJMYEMLZG45E/</a><br />\n<br />\n國際郵輪協會禁中港澳客登船<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200209/large/1581180803_d3e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200209%2Flarge%2F1581180803_d3e0.jpg&h=11fbfe52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n皇家加勒比旗下的海洋聖歌號，把23名中國乘客送返國。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】多艘豪華郵輪持續錄得武漢肺炎確診或疑似病例，會員佔全球經營率九成郵輪航線的國際郵輪協會（CLIA），前日起禁止14日內曾到中國、香港和澳門的人士登船，其他乘客如14日內曾接觸確診或疑似確診病人，同樣不准上船，以保障乘客和船員的健康。皇家加勒比國際郵輪公司（Royal Caribbean）與挪威郵輪（Norwegian Cruise Lines）更禁止所有中、港、澳人士登船。<br />\n<br />\n國際郵輪協會表示，被禁上船人士應自行與郵輪公司及旅行社商討退款，船上必須配備醫療設施，並且有醫療專業人員提供24小時服務，以便向客人提供初步醫療服務，防止疾病傳播。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n登船前或需再檢疫<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：隔離夫婦對港府hea做感洩氣<br />\n<br />\n協會會員之一的皇家加勒比國際郵輪公司，宣佈2月7日起，一律禁止持有中國、香港或澳門護照的旅客登船；所有曾經接觸過15日內到訪中港澳人士的旅客，以及感到不適或出現感冒病徵的旅客，登船前要進行額外檢疫，發燒或血氧含量過低的旅客會被禁止登船。<br />\n<br />\n皇家加勒比旗下的海洋聖歌號（Anthem of the Seas），上周四通報船上有中國乘客曾發燒，周五停泊美國新澤西州後，四名中國乘客需送院隔離，23名中國乘客直送機場，返回中國，暫時未有人確診。<br />\n<br />\n挪威郵輪同樣禁止持中港澳護照人士登船，新政策亦規定在啟程前30天內從中國（包括港澳）的機場出發、轉機或到過上述機場的客人，不得登船。<br />\n<br />\n此外，曾於2月1日停泊香港並被日本拒絕入境的郵輪威士特丹號，現時船上有29人來自香港，11人來自中國，所屬荷美郵輪昨日公佈，指郵輪目前正在台灣沿海西南路線航行，嘗試尋找最適合港口停泊讓乘客下船，又稱正與不同的政府合作解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林于鈴、陳詠恩"},{"pid":"0069a323e4a0b34b59f77503284ac438c3d813b9","tid":1871040,"uid":53122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:25:43.000Z","msg":"淋病唔封關<br />\n<br />\n攬炒成功"},{"pid":"ece47aed92b1809645e0c9dfc025e53081030491","tid":1871040,"uid":3020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:28:56.000Z","msg":"攬炒之母"},{"pid":"6a183856f842631b50501f20af85a46a426c80cb","tid":1871040,"uid":248290,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E4eseTf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE4eseTf.gif&h=e773722d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d2acd69322179ee9f7f29843924264e34604b16","tid":1871040,"uid":254788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:32:57.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5536c471f11eec06fe3bd9e06d52b33746eca977","tid":1871040,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"共享中國人榮耀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcaf2f3427f0c3bf66296495532deaceeb31bb0c","tid":1871040,"uid":205927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:34:54.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e0778cce66dd7b57d85b873b25387422048991","tid":1871040,"uid":121125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T08:39:25.000Z","msg":"做得好 唔好散播病毒啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c01ea1cb34e8876bc49a935909ac959898326fc","tid":1871040,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite